---
import OrbitMark from './OrbitMark.astro';

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const links = [
  { href: '/', label: '首頁' },
  { href: '/about', label: '關於我們' },
  { href: '/products', label: '產品' },
  { href: '/contact', label: '聯絡我們' },
];
---

<footer class="border-t border-ink-line bg-ink-soft">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-14 lg:px-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <OrbitMark size={36} />
          <div class="leading-tight">
            <p class="font-display text-base font-bold text-paper">Dongyu Tech</p>
            <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-muted">動域科技</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
          結合軟體、硬體與 AI 能力,將創新構想轉化為真正可落地的產品與服務。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:gap-16">
        <nav>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-faint">
            導覽
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
            {
              links.map((l) => (
                <li>
                  <a
                    href={l.href}
                    class="text-sm text-muted transition-colors hover:text-paper"
                  >
                    {l.label}
                  </a>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>
        </nav>

        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-faint">
            聯絡
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-muted">
            <li>
              <a
                href="mailto:dongyu.company@gmail.com"
                class="transition-colors hover:text-orbit"
              >
                dongyu.company@gmail.com
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>動域科技股份有限公司</li>
            <li>Dongyu Tech</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-12 flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-ink-line pt-6 text-xs text-faint sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"
    >
      <p>© {year} 動域科技股份有限公司. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>打造下一代智慧產品體驗</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
